- `git add log.md && git commit -m "log(autofix): fix reverted — tests failed [autofix]" && git push origin {{ push_branch }}`
- **Continue the loop** — do NOT exit

**m. IF TESTS PASS (or no test suite found) — commit, push, verify:**

